title: HP MSA 2040: Temperature of all Disks
agents: hp_msa
catalog: hw/storagehw/hp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the hightest, lowest and average temperature
 of all disks of a HP MSA 2040 storage system. To make it work
 you have to configure the hp_msa datasource program via WATO.

 Furthermore it displays the number of temperature sensors.

 The levels are configurable.
 Upper levels are set to 40 and 45 celsius.

item:
 The fixed statement {{Disks}}

discovery:
 One service is created.
